'''Light side artifacts''' were ancient weapons and tools used by the [[Jedi/Legends|Jedi]] and other organizations dedicated to the use of the [[Light side of the Force/Legends|Light side of the Force]]. They were used to enhance and/or assist the user's ability to channel [[The Force/Legends|the Force]] to attain their desired goals.

